    <title>上海之行</title>
    <url>/p/42399.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="/assets/js/Meting.min.js"></script><p>记录我们第一次旅行～</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h3 id="1-2019-9-13："><a href="#1-2019-9-13：" class="headerlink" title="1.2019.9.13："></a>1.2019.9.13：</h3><p>在学校上完课就直奔机场啦～</p>
<img src="/p/42399/1.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<!-- more -->

<img src="/p/42399/2.jpg" class="" title="This is an image">

<p>晚上到了酒店太饿了，去吃了<a href="http://www.dianping.com/shop/isZAHlfHjag4yBFJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">哥哥的深夜食堂</a>，强烈安利，超级好吃！<br>吃到什么都不剩才想起来拍照😂</p>
<img src="/p/42399/3.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<h3 id="2-2019-9-14："><a href="#2-2019-9-14：" class="headerlink" title="2.2019.9.14："></a>2.2019.9.14：</h3><p>早上6:30就赶到了迪士尼，早享卡至关重要，不买的话只能排排排了…</p>
<img src="/p/42399/4.jpg" class="" title="This is an image">

<p>因为买了早享卡进门抢了快速通行证，所以全天下来没有任何排队的时候，甚至3刷了加勒比海盗船^ ^</p>
<img src="/p/42399/5.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<img src="/p/42399/7.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<h3 id="3-2019-9-15"><a href="#3-2019-9-15" class="headerlink" title="3.2019.9.15:"></a><strong>3.2019.9.15:</strong></h3><p>不得不吐槽上海地铁真的又破又长，一大早坐地铁的感受属实拉垮</p>
<p>跟上海中心一比的话，东方明珠确实不行，又矮又贵</p>
<img src="/p/42399/8.jpg" class="" title="This is an image">
<img src="/p/42399/9.jpg" class="" title="This is an image">

<p>下午和晚上：</p>
<img src="/p/42399/10.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<img src="/p/42399/11.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

<h3 id="4-2019-9-16"><a href="#4-2019-9-16" class="headerlink" title="4.2019.9.16:"></a>4.2019.9.16:</h3><p>吃了早餐顺带敲了一节早上的课，回学校咯</p>
<img src="/p/42399/12.jpg" class="" title="This is an image">

<img src="/p/42399/13.JPG" class="" title="This is an image">

]]></content>
